wiki.summary: "Dead Trollz" is a diss track on King Von. YoungBoy and King Von had a beef before Von's passing. King Von wanted a feature from YB but YB denied. After that, Von was trolling YoungBoy (he posted a post on his Instagram saying some shit about YB - of course he didn't officially mark it, but it was certainly directed to YB). YoungBoy responded on his Instagram post under photo with his son "Imma make sure my son fuck yo daughter". "Pussy nigga drove that he can't get no feature" this line is literally about Von. wiki.content: "Dead Trollz" is a diss track on King Von. YoungBoy and King Von had a beef before Von's passing. King Von wanted a feature from YB but YB denied. After that, Von was trolling YoungBoy (he posted a post on his Instagram saying some shit about YB - of course he didn't officially mark it, but it was certainly directed to YB). YoungBoy responded on his Instagram post under photo with his son "Imma make sure my son fuck yo daughter". "Pussy nigga drove that he can't get no feature" this line is literally about Von. After Von's passing some lines started to be more mysterious then it did before: "That nigga dead, tell me did he move? / All that he said was, "Watch the news" / Talkin' turnin' out, he done turned to two / It was two victims ain't make it through", "Plan on stainin' somethin' in Atlanta too" - we know Von was shot in Atlanta and two other victims passed in a shooting. Was it all planned? We'll never know... "[...] he way from the Bulls home" Read more on Last.fm.
